00:00:12.966 --> 00:00:17.681
Hi! Welcome to your favorite cookery show Aha Emi Ruchi

00:00:31.152 --> 00:00:32.813
What are you going to cook for us today?
Cholay Batura

00:00:49.425 --> 00:00:51.591
Ingredients required for Cholay Batura

00:00:51.715 --> 00:01:05.899
Chick Peas, Cumin Seeds, Mustard Seeds, 
Bengal Gram, Green Chillies, Onions, Ginger Garlic Paste,
 Turmeric Powder, Red Chilli Powder, Cholay Masala,
 Tomato Puree, Coriander Leaves, Salt &amp; Oil

00:01:15.242 --> 00:01:22.892
First soak some chick peas in water and let them stay overnight

00:01:31.336 --> 00:01:47.607
Now take a pan and boil the soaked chick peas 
with some salt and a tea bag in it for 15 minutes

00:02:09.622 --> 00:02:14.162
Heat five spoons of oil in a pan

00:02:31.380 --> 00:02:36.708
Add some custard seeds, mustard seeds and bengal gram into the pan

00:02:39.383 --> 00:02:44.224
Add some sliced green chillies into the pan

00:02:49.357 --> 00:02:57.547
Add one cup of chopped onions into the pan

00:03:08.342 --> 00:03:12.818
Let them fry for a while, until the onions
 turn into golden brown in colour

00:03:17.615 --> 00:03:24.441
Add one spoon of ginger garlic paste
 in to the pan &amp; let it fry for a while

00:03:38.323 --> 00:03:42.597
Add half spoon of turmeric powder
into the pan &amp; mix well

00:03:49.628 --> 00:03:54.462
Add two spoons of red chilli powder
 into the pan &amp; mix well

00:04:04.478 --> 00:04:11.108
Now add the boiled chick peas into the pan &amp; mix well

00:04:17.704 --> 00:04:21.901
Add some salt into the pan &amp; mix well

00:04:43.697 --> 00:04:52.617
Add one cup of tomato puree into the pan &amp; mix well

00:05:10.582 --> 00:05:17.263
Now let it cook for 3 minutes

00:05:37.601 --> 00:05:45.827
Add one spoon of cholay masala into the pan &amp; mix well

00:06:03.089 --> 00:06:08.559
Add some coriander leaves into the pan &amp; mix well

00:06:35.263 --> 00:06:41.852
Take the Cholay Batura into a serving bowl

00:06:42.521 --> 00:06:46.658
Now top the dish with some coriander leaves

